<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ewr
                                <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> sey, daz wir den
                                <expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sie auf einen
                                <expan>genante<ex>n</ex></expan> tag czü uns
                            <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>, darauf ir ewr frewnde auch
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> czü uns
                            <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Sweinfürt, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sie
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ir erber botscheft czü uns czeschicken
                        auf den <app><note><q type="date">montag als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> hewt über acht tag</q>06.05.1409</note></app> <add>cze
                            ratczeit</add>; darnach wiszet ew <expan>czericht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> auch also her czü uns
                                <expan>czeschick<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
